        "channel": 0,
        "lyrics": [
          "J'aime\n l'E\n-ter\n-nel,\n car\n Il\n en\n-tend\n ma\n voix;\n\rIl\n a\n pen\n-ché\n son\n o\n-reil\n-le\n vers\n moi;\n\rje\n l'in\n-vo\n-que\n-rai\n tou\n-te\n ma\n vie.\n\rJ'aime\n l'E\n-ter\n-nel,\n j'aime\n l'E\n-ter\n-nel.\n\nIl\n a\n dé\n-li\n-vré\n mon\n âme\n de\n la\n mort,\n\rmes\n yeux\n des\n lar\n-mes,\n\rmes\n pieds\n de\n la\n chu\n-te.\n\rL'E\n-ter\n-nel\n est\n mi\n-sé\n-ri\n-cor\n-di\n-eux\n et\n jus\n-te,\n\rIl\n est\n plein\n de\n com\n-pas\n-sion."
        ],
